cker%2C%20completely%20changes%20a%20walk.%20My%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdaily-hour-long-walk-impacts-2020-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elunchtime%20stroll%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20replaced%20by%20a%20challenging%20workout%20that%20raised%20my%20heart%20rate%20and%20left%20me%20so%20sweaty%20I%20needed%20to%20shower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20tried%20rucking%20a%20few%20times%20now%2C%20I%20can%20understand%20why%20it's%20a%20brilliant%20way%20to%20improve%20your%20fitness%2C%20but%20it's%20definitely%20not%20relaxing%20like%20a%20regular%20walk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222750b261-bca9-439e-b1ff-9ebdcbb5813e%5C%22%3EProper%20rucking%20equipment%20is%20pricey%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20used%20GoRuck's%2015L%20Rucker%204.0%20with%20one%20of%20the%20brand's%2020-pound%20plates%20in%20the%20inside%20pocket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20GoRuck%20rucker%20backpack%20and%20weight%20plate.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6699363349138fa6f6e3742c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20rucking%20kit%20used%20by%20Rachel%20Hosie.%3Cp%3ERachel%20Hosie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20backpack%20is%20designed%20to%20hold%20both%20a%20weight%20plate%20and%20have%20space%20for%20other%20items%20like%20a%20bottle%20of%20water%2C%20an%20extra%20layer%20of%20clothing%2C%20and%20snacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rucker%20alone%20costs%20%24245%20and%20the%20plate%20costs%20%24105%2C%20so%20they're%20not%20cheap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20products%20have%20a%20lifetime%20warranty%20and%20are%20designed%20specifically%20for%20rucking.%20To%20minimize%20injury%20and%20improve%20posture%2C%20the%20weight%20stays%20closer%20to%20your%20body%20and%20higher%20up%20your%20back%20than%20if%20you%20just%20put%20heavy%20things%20in%20a%20normal%20backpack%2C%20and%20the%20bag%20has%20thickly%20padded%20shoulder%20and%20sternum%20straps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20colors%20to%20choose%20from%2C%20and%20I%20opted%20for%20a%20berry%20shade%2C%20which%20I%20thought%20was%20very%20cute%20and%20on%20brand%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWalking%20around%20with%20the%20ruck%20on%20definitely%20doesn't%20look%20as%20odd%20as%20wearing%20a%20weighted%20vest.%20That%20said%2C%20it%20doesn't%20look%20like%20a%20normal%20backpack%2C%20so%20I%20did%20get%20a%20few%20strange%20looks%20as%20I%20strolled%20around%20the%20rural%20village%20where%20I%20live%20on%20a%20weekday%20lunchtime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20felt%20very%20different%20from%20carrying%20a%20normal%20backpack%2C%20too%2C%20likely%20due%20to%20the%20weight%20and%20its%20positioning.%20I%20often%20find%20myself%20carrying%20a%20decent%20amount%20of%20weight%20on%20my%20back%2C%20whether%20that's%20dashing%20around%20London%20with%20my%20laptop%2C%20water%2C%20and%20overnight%20essentials%2C%20or%20heading%20off%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshould-you-rock-climb-instead-of-normal-gym-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20long%20hike%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20my%20far-more-outdoorsy%20fianc%C3%A9.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f252b5c7-7b56-48bc-90a8-8aeb800c2211%5C%22%3ERucking%20raised%20my%20heart%20rate%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rachel%20Hosie%20walking%20outside%20while%20wearing%20a%20ruck.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669936d280d4d5da13d4f713%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERucking%20swiftly%20raised%20my%20heart%20rate.%3Cp%3ERachel%20Hosie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20some%20fiddling%20around%20with%20the%20straps%20to%20find%20the%20right%20positioning.%20The%20rucker%20wasn't%20particularly%20comfortable%2C%20especially%20as%20I%20got%20sweatier%20and%20sweatier.%20And%20boy%2C%20did%20I%20get%20sweaty.%20I%20wasn't%20expecting%20to%20need%20a%20shower%20afterward%2C%20but%20I%20definitely%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELoosening%20the%20straps%20meant%20my%20back%20could%20breathe%20somewhat%20(I%20didn't%20love%20the%20feeling%20of%20my%20sweaty%20back%20on%20the%20rucker)%2C%20but%20it%20also%20meant%20the%20weight%20moved%20around%20and%20hit%20my%20back%20with%20every%20step%2C%20which%20wasn't%20great.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20each%20ruck%20I've%20done%2C%20I've%20swiftly%20felt%20my%20heart%20rate%20increase%20to%20what%20felt%20like%20higher%20than%20during%20a%20normal%20walk%2C%20so%20I%20could%20tell%20my%20body%20was%20working%20hard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%2020%20minutes%20or%20so%2C%20I%20could%20feel%20my%20upper%20body%20and%20shoulders%20fatiguing.%20After%20half%20an%20hour%20or%20so%2C%20I%20feel%20myself%20starting%20to%20tire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERucking%2C%20I%20have%20learned%2C%20doesn't%20help%20you%20relax%20and%20decompress%20like%20a%20walk%20might.%20It's%20a%20workout.%20And%20one%20I%20should%20not%20attempt%20immediately%20after%20eating%20my%20lunch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20learned%20that%20the%20ruck%20isn't%20something%20I%20will%20just%20always%20throw%20on%20when%20going%20for%20my%20daily%20walk.%20When%20I%20want%20to%20get%20a%20full%20body%20workout%20in%20while%20enjoying%20the%20outdoors%2C%20I%20will%20ruck%2C%20when%20I%20need%20to%20decompress%2C%20I%20will%20walk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a0bdfb1d-931d-4b0f-af20-553648a4751d%5C%22%3EThe%20ruck%20is%20useful%20for%20workouts%20too%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20weekday%20evening%20I%20told%20myself%20I'd%20go%20for%20a%20ruck%2C%20but%20what%20I%20really%20wanted%20to%20do%20was%20watch%20Wimbledon.%20So%20I%20decided%20I'd%20get%20the%20best%20of%20both%20worlds%20and%20exercise%20in%20front%20of%20the%20television%20while%20wearing%20the%20rucker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20ended%20up%20being%20a%20great%20workout%2C%20and%20defin