%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20recounted%20the%20story%20of%20a%20friend%20who%20decided%20to%20get%20surgery%20at%20a%20private%20Iranian%20hospital%20after%20being%20put%20off%20by%20horror%20stories%20about%20the%20public%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20surgery%2C%20the%20friend%20was%20unable%20to%20afford%20a%20stay%20in%20the%20hospital%2C%20so%20he%20checked%20himself%20into%20a%20motel%2C%20Soheil%20said.%20%26quot%3BHe%20called%20one%20of%20his%20friends%2C%20saying%20that%20he%20didn't%20feel%20OK%2C%26quot%3B%20Soheil%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20his%20friend%20went%2C%20he%20had%20passed%20away.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20a%20trans%20haven%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20ridiculed%20and%20othered%20is%20common%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falireza-fazeli-monfared-iran-gay-man-beheaded-family-honor-killing-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIran's%20LGBTQ%2B%20populations%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20Varamini%2C%20the%20transgender%20man%20who%20had%20his%20surgery%20paid%20for%20by%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20why%2C%20after%20his%20own%20transition%2C%20he%20worked%20with%20the%20State%20Welfare%20Organization%20of%20Iran%20to%20offer%20support%20to%20fellow%20transgender%20Iranians.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20he%20established%20his%20own%20organization%2C%20the%20Mahtaa%20Institute%2C%20which%20provides%20clandestine%20support%20to%20LBGTQ%2B%20communities%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsex-work-linkedin-arielle-egozi-essay-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esex%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20(He%20said%20the%20government%20heavily%20monitors%20his%20organization.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Varamini%20is%20grateful%20for%20his%20transition%2C%20he's%20confronted%20daily%20by%20the%20harsh%20realities%20others%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIran%20does%20offer%20opportunities%20for%20some%20transgender%20individuals%2C%20he%20said%2C%20but%20for%20many