20she%20walked%20down%20the%20aisle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EJennifer%20Lee%20has%20loved%20fashion%20since%20her%20mom%20taught%20her%20how%20to%20sew%20when%20she%20was%20just%206%20years%20old.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jennifer%20Lee%20and%20her%20mother%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668ffb15b2528216eeb55ceb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222666%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELee%20with%20her%20mother%20on%20her%20wedding%20day.%20%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Lee%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELee%20was%20a%20competitive%20ice%20skater%20from%206%20to%2016%20and%20worked%20with%20her%20mom%20to%20create%20costumes%20for%20her%20programs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20first%20started%20ice%20skating%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20outfits%20that%20I%20wanted%20didn't%20really%20exist.%20If%20you%20wanted%20something%20that%20was%20really%20elegant%20and%20showed%20great%20movement%20and%20grace%2C%20it%20was%20meant%20for%20Olympic%20skaters%2C%26quot%3B%20Lee%20recalled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20mom%20taught%20me%20how%20to%20help%20her%20create%20these%20costumes%20to%20make%20our%20programs%20come%20alive%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20the%20most%20fond%20memories%20of%20staying%20up%20late%20with%20my%20mom%2C%20bedazzling%20crystals%20on%20my%20dress%20in%20hopes%20to%20really%20glimmer%20in%20competition.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Lee%20went%20to%20UCLA%2C%20she%20joined%20the%20university's%20fashion%20club%20to%20keep%20learning%20new%20skills%20and%20techniques%20while%20pursuing%20a%20degree%20in%20bioengineering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20designed%20four%20collections%20in%20four%20years%20for%20our%20annual%20fashion%20show%20and%2C%20through%20that%2C%20kind%20of%20honed%20my%20craft%2C%26quot%3B%20Lee%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20was%20before%20YouTube%2C%20so%20I%20would%20take%20patterns%20from%20Joann%20Fabric%20and%20reconstruct%20them%20to%20create%20different%20garments.%20I%20learned%20how%20to%20pattern%20through%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELee's%20designs%20took%20a%20backseat%20as%20she%20pursued%20a%20career%20in%20cosmetics%20innovation.%20But%20after%20getting%20engaged%2C%20she%20dusted%20off%20her%20old%20sewing%20machine.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jen%20Lee%20kissing%20Brian%20at%20the%20altar%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668838f0268f62ba18a7d531%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222666%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELee%20with%20her%20husband%20Brian%20Shea%20on%20their%20wedding%20day.%20%3Cp%3EJose%20Villa%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELee%20met%20Brian%20Shea%20at%20a%20club%20in%20Barcelona%2C%20where%20his%20dance%20moves%20immediately%20caught%20her%20eye.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBrian%20is%20pretty%20tall%2C%20so%20he%20was%20all%20limbs%20on%20the%20dance%20floor%2C%20and%20I%20found%20that%20really%20endearing%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20with%20a%20laugh.%20%26quot%3BWe%20stayed%20up%20chatting%20all%20night.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20instant%20friendship%20became%20a%20long-distance%20relationship%20for%20three-and-a-half%20years%20before%20Shea%20left%20Chicago%20behind%20and%20joined%20Lee%20in%20NYC%20just%20before%20COVID%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELee%20had%20rediscovered%20her%20love%20for%20ice%20skating%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20and%20Shea%20would%20sometimes%20join%20her%20before%20work.%20He'd%20do%20laps%20in%20his%20hockey%20skates%20around%20the%20rink%20at%20Bryant%20Park%20while%20she%20worked%20on%20jumps%20and%20spins.%20So%20Lee%20thought%20nothing%20of%20it%20when%20he%20decided%20to%20join%20her%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20February%2022%2C%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20like%206%3A30%20a.m.%20and%20maybe%2020%20degrees%2C%20so%20nobody%20was%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Lee%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20thought%20we%20were%20going%20to%20start%20a%20little%20dance%20routine%2C%20and%20he%20went%20down%20to%20tie%20his%20hockey%20skate%2C%20but%20in%20reality%2C%20he%20got%20down%20on%20one%20knee%20and%20proposed.%20It%20was%20perfect.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELee%20had%20already%20returned%20to%20one%20of%20her%20childhood%20passions.%20As%20she%20began%20planning%20her%20wedding%2C%20she%20knew%20she%20wanted%20to%20return%20to%20fashion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20it%20being%20so%20personal%20and%20bringing%20together%20everyone%20I%20love%2C%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20the%20perfect%20opportunity%20to%20develop%20my%20first%20really%20cohesive%20collection%20for%20my%20family%20and%20friends%20%E2%80%94%20and%20my%20first%20bridal%20collection%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIt%20took%20Lee%20more%20than%20a%20year%20to%20make%20her%20six%20bridesmaid%20dresses.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jen%20Lee%20with%20her%20bridesmaids%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6688380a1aace5b3ada4c713%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELee%20with%20her%20bridesmaids%20in%20their%20custom%20dresses.%20%3Cp%3EJose%20Villa%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20called%20the%20bag%20lady%20for%20probably%2014%20months%20leading%20up%20to%20my%20wedding%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20show%20up%20to%20work%20with%20a%20wheelie%20bag%20filled%20with%20patterns%20and%20fabric.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENearly%20every%20night%20after%20work%2C%20Lee%20would%20head%20straight%20from%20her%20office%20to%20the%20Fashion%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20where%20she'd%20sew%20or%20make%20patterns%20from%206%20p.m.%20to%20midnight.%20She%20approximates%20that%20the%20materials%20for%20each%20dress%20%E2%80%94%20all%20made%20with%20small-batch%20fabric%20%E2%80%94%20cost%20around%20%24500.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20always%20get%20it%20right%2C%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BSo%20there%20were%20times%20I'd%20have%20to%20get%20new%20fabric%20and%20start%20over%20and%20figure%20it%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%5CnThe%20dresses%20were%20inspired%20by%20%26quot%3BBridgerton%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20fit%20perfectly%20with%20the%20venue's%20garden%20setting.%20But%20Lee%20didn't%20want%20them%20to%20be%20traditional.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jen%20Lee's%20bridesmaid%20dresses%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668838201f0c1cd6d731ea16%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELee's%20bridesmaid%20dresses%20were%20inspired%20by%20the%20Regency%20Era%2C%20but%20they%20featured%20modern%20cutouts.%20%3Cp%3EJose%20Villa%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELee%20incorporated%20modern%20side%20and%20back%20cutouts%20or%20shoulder-baring%20silhouettes%20to%20make%20the%20dresses%20feel%20contemporary.%20She%20also%20kept%20the%20collection%20cohesive%20by%20sticking%20to%20a%20pastel%20palette%2C%20encouraging%20her%20friends%20to%20try%20colors%20they%20had%20never%20worn%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20trendy%20now%20to%20understand%20if%20you're%20a%20warm%20or%20cool%20tone%2C%20but%20as%20a%20designer%2C%20that's%20something%20I've%20always%20kept%20in%20mind%2C%26quot%3B%20Lee%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20knowing%20if%20my%20friends%20were%20warm%20or%20cool%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20push%20them%20a%20little%20bit%20and%20put%20them%20in%20a%20color%20palette%20that%20was%20unexpected.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20bridesmaids%20were%20excited%20to%20see%20themselves%20in%20colors%20that%20are%20maybe%20outside%20their%20day-to-day%20wear%20but%20still%20made%20them%20look%20beautiful%20and%20radiant%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BThey%20knew%20it%20was%20very%20much%20a%20fusion%20of%20their%20personality%20and%20my%20personality%20and%20our%20friendship%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESince%20most%20of%20Lee's%20bridesmaids%20lived%20in%20LA%20or%20San%20Francisco%2C%20she%20had%20to%20navigate%20making%20the%20dresses%20without%20many%20fittings.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jen%20Lee's%20bridesmaids%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6688529a1aace5b3ada4cf78%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELee%20stuck%20to%20pastel%20colors%20so%20her%20collection%20would%20still%20feel%20cohesive%2C%20even%20with%20mixed%20fabrics.%20%3Cp%3EJose%20Villa%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20time%20I%20flew%20home%20to%20plan%20the%20wedding%2C%20I%20would%20pack%20my%20muslin%20samples%20and%20different%20fabrics%20so%20I%20could%20shape%20and%20make%20sure%20the%20fabrics%20complemented%20their%20different%20skin%20tones%2C%26quot%3B%20Lee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELee%20also%20had%20to%20learn%20to%20make%20edits%20on%20the%20fly%20as%20some%20of%20her%20bridesmaids%20became%20pregnant%20or%20new%20moms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20meant%20so%20much%20to%20me%20to%20get%20the%20fit%20right%20and%20make%20sure%20that%20they%20felt%20comfortable%2C%26quot%3B%20Lee%20said.%20%26quot%3BMy%20friends%20have%20been%20there%20for%20me%20through%20the%20ups%20and%20downs%20of%20a%20long-distance%20relationship%20and%20all%20the%20heartbreaks%20before%20I%20met%20Brian%2C%20so%20it%20was%20important%20to%20me%20that%20they%20loved%20the%20dresses.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20bridesmaids'%20custom%20getting-ready%20outfits%20were%20also%20part%20of%20Lee's%2026-piece%20wedding%20collection.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jen%20Lee%20with%20her%20bridesmaids%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668837bf1aace5b3ada4c6fe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22