y%20probably%20wouldn't%20work%20out%20at%20all%20if%20they%20didn't%20with%20her%2C%20but%20paying%20for%20a%20personal%20trainer%20incentivizes%20them.%20People%20who%20don't%20have%20personal%20trainers%20can%20get%20the%20same%20effect%20by%20working%20out%20with%20friends%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22751f97ef-49f8-4491-8f1a-7defa9c043c2%5C%22%3EThey're%20positive%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20which%20came%20first%2C%20the%20exercise%20or%20the%20positivity%2C%20or%20vice%20versa%2C%26quot%3B%20Hurst%20said%2C%20but%20most%20of%20the%20people%20her%20clients%20are%20very%20positive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BExercise%20certainly%20helps%20with%20mood%2C%20and%20it%20helps%20with%20depression%20and%20anxiety%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20A%202020%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC7369812%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%20the%20International%20Journal%20of%20Environmental%20Research%20and%20Public%20Health%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20found%20that%20people%20who%20were%20more%20physically%20active%20tended%20to%20be%20happier%20and%20more%20satisfied%20with%20their%20lives%20than%20those%20who%20did%20less%20physical%20activity.%20A%202024%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bmj.com%2Fcontent%2F384%2Fbmj-2023-075847%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%20The%20BMJ%20meanwhile%20found%20that%20exercise%20appeared%20to%20be%20an%20effective%20treatment%20for%20all%20types%20of%20depression.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a4e75d42-1464-4e85-9386-f56c70b2d417%5C%22%3EThey're%20high-achieving%20and%20competitive%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20Hurst's%20clients%20are%20or%20were%20high-achieving%2C%20%26quot%3Bcompetitive%20business%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20take%20that%20attitude%20to%20their%20training%2C%20and%20they%20want%20to%20be%20fit%20and%20healthy%20for%20as%20long%20as%