ne%202024%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D3fa782bb94f5e3dfe721c8c2f8948bdfdfc5068cf5b93bbc11480a1236a8e167%26postID%3D6697c6cdc79d31931d78ce1c%26postSlug%3Dwhy-you-should-enter-work-history-job-application-already-resume-2024-7%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.flexjobs.com%252Fblog%252Fpost%252Fjob-ghosting-and-modern-hiring-practices-flexjobs-report%252F%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurvey%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%202%2C000%20US-based%20professionals%20by%20FlexJobs%20and%20MyPerfectResume%2C%2079%25%20said%20their%20biggest%20%26quot%3Bturn-off%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20job%20application%20is%20having%20to%20re-enter%20their%20work%20history%20after%20uploading%20a%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20tedious%20as%20it%20may%20be%2C%20there's%20a%20good%20reason%20you%20should%20still%20fill%20it%20out%20anyway.%20If%20you've%20ever%20just%20left%20it%20blank%20or%20typed%20%26quot%3BSee%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20hopes%20a%20hiring%20manager%20would%20consult%20that%20instead%2C%20you%20may%20be%20hurting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-job-bad-job-interviews-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyour%20chances%20of%20getting%20an%20interview%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20for%20this%20mostly%20comes%20down%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjobseeker-whose-resume-rejected-changed-format-to-help-search-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eapplicant-tracking%20systems%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20upload%20your%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20and%20it's%20parsed%2C%20and%20then%20you%20have%20to%20reenter%20some%20of%20the%20information%2C%20that%20allows%20for%20that%20information%20to%20be%20viewed%20correctly%20by%20the%20applicant-tracking%20system%20in%20terms%20of%20scanning%20for%20keywords%20and%20experience%20that%20the%20role%20is%20requiring%2C%26quot%3B