en%2C%20who%20runs%20the%20workplace%20advice%20website%20Ask%20a%20Manager%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.askamanager.org%2F2023%2F04%2Fis-it-bad-to-write-see-resume-in-online-application-systems.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20subject%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFortunately%2C%20filling%20out%20these%20fields%20can%20be%20as%20simple%20as%20copying%20and%20pasting%20what's%20already%20in%20your%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGreen%20added%20in%20her%20post%20that%20besides%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-this-is-an-excellent-resume-2013-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehaving%20a%20main%2C%20formatted%20version%20of%20your%20resume%20ready%20for%20applications%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it's%20helpful%20to%20also%20keep%20a%20plain%20text%20version%20to%20transfer%20information%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMake%20sure%20that%20you%20have%20the%20same%20information%20in%20both%20places%20so%20that%20no%20matter%20what%20system%20employers%20are%20using%20or%20what%20they're%20looking%20at%2C%20they%20can%20see%20the%20appropriate%20information%20about%20your%20skills%2C%20experiences%2C%20and%20accomplishments%20to%20know%20that%20you%20are%20the%20right%20candidate%20for%20the%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Frana.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-you-should-enter-work-history-job-application-already-resume-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721467322000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66995c9349138fa6f6e391c6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-you-should-enter-work-history-job-application-already-resume-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It's%20a%20pain%20to%20enter%20your%20work%20history%20in%20a%20job%20application%20even%20though%20it's%20already%20on%20your%20r%C3%A9sum%C3