ank%5C%22%3Etechnology%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20believe%20it%20can%20and%20will%20improve%20our%20lives%2C%20unlock%20human%20potential%2C%20solve%20big%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20initially%2C%20I%20assumed%20that%20I'd%20love%20a%20vape%20that's%20also%20a%20phone.%20I%20was%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20first%20learned%20of%20the%20Swype%20vape%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fjimfredette32%2Fstatus%2F1809342175106523411%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esocial%20media%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20a%20few%20doctored%20images%20of%20its%20screen%20had%20gone%20viral.%20(Sadly%2C%20no%2C%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fdrunkyotes%2Fstatus%2F1809674467800473813%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecannot%20show%20you%3C%2Fa%3E%20Zillow.)%20It%20also%20came%20up%20on%20Reddit's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2Fdumbphones%2Fcomments%2F1dyv65u%2Fmy_new_dumb_phonevape_arrived%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Er%2Fdumbphone%3C%2Fa%3E%20discussion%20board%2C%20which%20is%20for%20people%20looking%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgave-up-iphone-dumb-light-phone-2-comparison-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emove%20away%20from%20the%20addicting%20glow%20of%20the%20smartphone%3C%2Fa%3E%20screen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20vape%2C%20but%20I%20%3Cem%3Eam%3C%2Fem%3E%20severely%20addicted%20to%20my%20phone.%20Perhaps%20I%20could%20swap%20one%20vice%20for%20another%2C%20or%20maybe%20just%20double%20down%20on%20both%20%E2%80%94%20or%20something.%20I'm%20not%20really%20sure%20what%20my%20plans%20were%20other%20than%20that%20I%20knew%20I%20simply%20must%20have%20this%20device%2C%20and%20I%20immediately%20ordered%20it%20from%20a%20site%20called%20General%20Vape.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20an%20obvious%20disclaimer%3A%20%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Insider%20does%20not%20endorse%20vaping%20or%20starting%20to%20vape%20simply%20because%20it%20seems%20like%20it%20would%20be%20funny%20to%20have%20a%20vape%20phone.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Swype%20vape%20is%20a%20nicotine%20vape%20(not%20weed%2C%20in%20case%20you%20were%20wondering)%20and%20comes%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20flavors%20like%20Blue%20Raspberry%2C%20Gum%20Mint%2C%20Pina%20Colada%2C%20Pink%20Burst%2C%20and%20%26quot%3BFucking%20Fab%26quot%3B%20(which%20was%20sadly%20sold%20out).%20I%20went%20with%20Watermelon%20Ice.%20(Samatha%20Cole%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.404media.co%2Ftwitter-internet-vape-touchscreen-swype%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E404%20Media%20also%20tried%20out%20the%20Swype%20vape%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20we%20didn't%20plan%20this.%20Coincidentally%2C%20we%20both%20got%20the%20same%20flavor.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20vape%20costs%20around%20%2420%2C%20comes%20prefilled%2C%20and%20is%20single-use%20and%20disposable.%20Yes%2C%20a%20disposable%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Swype%20vape%20and%20its%20screen%2C%20and%20a%20message%20on%20its%20screen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669934c349138fa6f6e37332%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESwype's%20screen%2C%20which%20shows%20the%20apps%20it%20can%20connect%20to%20(left)%2C%20and%20an%20actual%20notification%20(right)%20%E2%80%94%20in%20this%20case%2C%20from%20X.%3Cp%3EKatie%20Notopoulos%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cdf7d6cf-e9f0-47c2-ae1f-ce8923946563%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESwype%20uses%20Bluetooth%20to%20connect%20to%20your%20phone%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Swype%20does%2C%20indeed%2C%20feel%20like%20you%20got%20what%20you%20paid%20for%3A%20a%20%2420%20disposable%20phone%20that's%20also%20a%20vape.%20It's%20very%20janky%20in%20ways%20that%20you%20probably%20haven't%20encountered%20in%20modern%20electronics%2C%20which%2C%20for%20the%20most%20part%2C%20tend%20to%20actually%20work%20as%20advertised.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%20of%20all%2C%20it's%20not%20technically%20a%20phone.%20It%20works%20by%20syncing%20with%20your%20phone%20over%20Bluetooth.%20You%20can't%20actually%20take%20phone%20calls%20on%20it%20(it%20has%20no%20speakers%2C%20microphone%2C%20or%20cellular%20connection).%20You%20can%20tap%20it%20to%20answer%20a%20call%2C%20but%20it%20just%20picks%20up%20on%20your%20real%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20touchscreen%20does%20display%20notifications%20when%20you%20swipe%20up%20%E2%80%94%20I%20could%20see%20messages%20from%20Signal%2C%20news%20push%20alerts%2C%20X%20notifications%2C%20and%20texts.%20I%20have%20to%20say%2C%20there%20is%20something%20truly%20thrilling%20about%20reading%20a%20tweet%20on%20the%20side%20of%20a%20vape.%20(You%20can%20only%20see%20individual%20tweets%20that%20come%20to%20you%20as%20notifications%20%E2%80%94%20you%20can't%20scroll%20through%20your%20full%20X%20feed.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Swype%20vape%20phone%20device%20sits%20in%20my%20hand%20with%20a%20view%20of%20its%20home%20screen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66993e9efb2b6bedb0585752%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Swype%20vape%20phone's%20home%20screen%20is%20cluttered.%3Cp%3EKatie%20Notopoulos%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22242cb399-c7a4-4ff4-bf54-2fe6a14a07b7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20WearinOS%20app%20is%20very%20buggy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20none%20of%20this%20works%20very%20well.%20To%20set%20this%20all%20up%2C%20you%20need%20to%20download%20an%20app%20to%20your%20phone%20called%20%26quot%3BWearinOS.%26quot%3B%20This%20app%20seems%20designed%20not%20for%20the%20Swype%20vape%20but%20for%20some%20sort%20of%20wearable%20fitness%20tracker.%20(I%20forgot%20to%20mention%3A%20The%20Swype%20does%20also%20have%20a%20built-in%20fitness%20tracker%20so%20you%20can%20track%20your%20outdoor%20cycling%20while%20huffing%20down%20Watermelon%20Ice%20vape%20juice.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWearinOS%20is%20broken%20in%20strange%20and%20funny%20ways.%20There%20are%20elements%20of%20the%20app%20that%2C%20when%20you're%20using%20your%20iPhone%20to%20configure%20it%2C%20simply%20don't%20fit%20on%20an%20iPhone's%20screen%20%E2%80%94%20like%20the%20app%20wasn't%20properly%20formatted.%20There%20are%20buttons%20that%2C%20when%20you%20tap%20them%2C%20nothing%20happens%2C%20like%20the%20button%20to%20check%20for%20firmware%20updates.%20The%20weather%20feature%20crashed%20the%20app%20every%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221290%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Swype%20app%20home%20screen%20as%20seen%20on%20my%20iPhone%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66993c2a80d4d5da13d4fc3c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222796%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Swype%20app's%20home%20screen%20on%20my%20iPhone.%20The%20app%20seemed%20to%20be%20mostly%20for%20a%20fitness%20tracker%2C%20not%20my%20vape%20phone.%3Cp%3EKatie%20Notopoulos%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20using%20the%20touchscreen%20on%20the%20Swype%20itself%20also%20was%20really%20buggy.%20There%20were%20similar%20problems%20of%20trying%20to%20tap%20buttons%20that%20simply%20didn't%20seem%20to%20tap.%20Two%20video%20games%20came%20on%20the%20Swype%2C%20Aircraft%20Battle%20and%202048%2C%20which%20is%20a%20number%20tile%20game.%20But%202048%20didn't%20seem%20to%20work%20at%20all%20%E2%80%94%20you%20couldn't%20tap%20any%20of%20the%20tiles.%20(Samantha%20Cole%20had%20the%20same%20problem%20with%20this%20game%2C%20so%20it%20wasn't%20just%20my%20one%20device.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20elements%20didn't%20really%20work%20as%20you'd%20expect.%20For%20example%2C%20you%20could%20view%20some%20X%20posts%20and%20iMessages%2C%20but%20in%20reality%2C%20I%20just%20got%20a%20mirror%20of%20the%20push%20notifications%20I%20was%20getting%20on%20my%20phone%3A%20news%20alerts%2C%20some%20social%20alerts%2C%20iMessages%2C%20Signal%20messages%2C%20and%20even%20push%20alerts%20from%20the%20Target%20shopping%20app%20%E2%80%94%20all%20lumped%20together%2C%20and%20it%20was%20sometimes%20confusing%20to%20tell%20what%20app%20they%20were%20coming%20from.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20biggest%20issue%20was%20that%20the%20Swype%20just%20didn't%20seem%20to%20update%20reliably%20with%20new%20messages.%20I'm%20not%20sure%20if%20this%20was%20the%20Bluetooth%20connection%20dropping%20or%20some%20other%20issue.%20It%20went%20half%20a%20day%20without%20updating%20the%20notifications%2C%20and%20I%20could%20never%20figure%20out%20why%20exactly%20it%20did%20that%20or%20what%20eventually%20fixed%20the%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20worth%20noting%20that%20%26quot%3BWearinOS%26quot%3B%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.start.watches%26hl%3Den_US%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elisted%20on%20the%20Google%20App%20Store%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20owned%20by%20the%20Shenzhen%20Communication%20Technology%20Co.%20Just%20to%20be%20clear%3A%20I'm%20doing%20this%20for%20fun%2C%20and%20I%20wouldn't%20necessarily%20recommend%20you%20do%20the%20same.%20(I've%20contacted%20the%20company%2C%20which%20is%20based%20in%20China%2C%20for%20comment.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2226ae6840-c267-45a8-b3c2-0f7997c23004%5C%22%3EThe%20vaping%20experience%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20not%20a%20vaper%20(I%20tried%20a%20Juul%20years%20ago)%2C%20so%20my%20judgment%20on%20the%20actual%20vaping%20experience%20is%20limited.%20The%20Watermelon%20Ice%20scent%20was%20overwhelming%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20opened%20the%20package%3B%20my%20editor%20was%20convinced%20he%20had%20a%20contact%20high%20from%20it%20before%20anyone%20had%20even%20hit%20it.%20(I%20am%20not%20sure%20this%20is%20possible%2C%20but%20it%20DID%20smell.)%20%5BEditor's%20note%3A%20It%20%3Cem%3Eis%3C%2Fem%3E%20possible!%5D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20first%20hit%20was%20accidentally%20far%20too%20large.%20I%20had%20been%20trying%20to%20take%20a%20selfie%20to%20document%20my%20first%20puff%2C%20imagining%20I'd%20look%20cool.%20Instead%2C%20I%20snapped%20it%20just%20as%20my%20face%20was%20contorted%20in%20shock%20and%20disgust%20at%20the%20blast%20of%20watermelon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20guess%20is%20if%20you're%20a%20regular%20vaper%2C%20this%20is%20probably%20fine.%20It%20comes%20with%205%25%20nicotine%20juice%2C%20has%20three%20puff%20strength%20levels%2C%20and%20claims%20to%20last%20up%20to%2030%2C000%20puffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221182%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20grossed-out%20face%20of%20the%20author%20after%20she%20took%20a%20puff%20on%20the%20Swype%20vape.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66992c55fb2b6bedb05848b1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221572%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20meant%20to%20take%20a%20cool%20selfie%20of%20myself%20blowing%20out%20vapor%2C%20but%20my%20first%20puff%20caught%20me%20off%20guard.%3Cp%3EKatie%20Notopoulos%20%2F%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220009fea4-351f-4682-b14f-96e43bd571a2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20can%20it%20actually%20replace%20your%20phone%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETragically%2C%20for%20the%20brain-rotted%20nic%20fiends%20out%20there%2C%20the%20Swype%20isn't%20going%20to%20replace%20your%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bugginess%20of%20the%20Swype%20means%20that%20there's%20no%20way%20you%20could%20use%20it%20to%20replace%20or%20reliably%20supplement%20your%20phone.%20But%20I%20have%20hope%20%E2%80%94%20if%20it%20did%20actually%20work%20a%20little%20better%2C%20I%20could%20imagine%20that%20it%20might%20work%20as%20a%20way%20not%20to%20have%20to%20stare%20at%20your%20phone%20but%20still%20get%20important%20notifications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20of%20us%2C%20the%20temptation%20of%20the%20phone%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0getting%20sucked%20into%20checking%20email%20or%20scrolling%20Instagram%20when%20you%20meant%20just%20to%20check%20that%20text%20message%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0is%20strong.%20I%20like%20my%20Apple%20Watch%20for%20this%20reason%3A%20I%20know%20I'll%20get%20alerted%20about%20important%20things%20(calls%20and%20texts)%2C%20but%20I%20can%20leave%20my%20phone%20in%20my%20purse%20or%20the%20other%20room%20and%20not%20worry%20about%20checking%20it%20constantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20are%20feeling%20oppressed%20by%20their%20phones%2C%20looking%20for%20ways%20to%20claw%20back%20some%20of%20their%20brain%20space%20and%20break%20the%20dopamine%20cycle%20of%20idly%20scrolling.%20%26quot%3BDumb%20phones%26quot%3B%20are%20becoming%20popular.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flight-dumb-phone-increasingly-like-iphone-including-the-price-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Light%20Phone%2C%20a%20%24300%20dumbphone%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20only%20makes%20calls%20and%20texts%20with%20no%20extra%20apps%20aside%20from%20an%20alarm%20and%20calendar%2C%20has%20become%20a%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20friend%20of%20mine%2C%20frustrated%20with%20how%20she%20always%20felt%20distracted%20by%20her%20phone%2C%20replaced%20her%20iPhone%20with%20the%20Light%20Phone.%20She%20made%20it%20two%20days%20before%20giving%20up%20and%20going%20back%20to%20her%20smartphone.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20impossible%20to%20be%20a%20human%20without%20a%20smartphone%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20me.%20(Business%20Insider's%20Jordan%20Hart%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgave-up-iphone-dumb-light-phone-2-comparison-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eonly%20made%20it%20a%20week%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20Light%20Phone%20before%20she%20came%20back%20to%20reality.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrankly%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20time%20we%20start%20expecting%20more%20from%20our%20smartphones.%20Why%20%3Cem%3Ecan't%3C%2Fem%3E%20my%20iPhone%20also%20provide%20me%20with%20a%20hit%20of%20melon-flavored%20nicotine%3F%20Tim%20Cook%2C%20you%20need%20to%20dream%20bigger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvape-phone-swype-replace-smartphone-dumb-phone-iphone-review-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721467022000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66993dff49138fa6f6e37a9f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvape-phone-swype-replace-smartphone-dumb-phone-iphone-review-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22What%20if%20you%20could%20vape%20AND%20text%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20all%20on%20one%20device.%20Would%20that%20replace%20my%20iPhone%3F%20I%20tried%20it%20to%20find%20out.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22knotopoulos%40businessinsider.com%20(Katie%20Notopoulos)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvape-phone-swype-replace-smartphone-dumb-phone-iphone-review-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Panel%20Of%20IAS%20Officers%20To%20Tackle%20Stray%20Dog%20Menace%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20government%20has%20appointed%20seven%20senior%20IAS%20officers%20to%20manage%20the%20escalating%20stray%20dog%20menace%20across%20the%20state.%20The%20stray%20dog%20crisis%20has%20become%20a%20significant%20concern%2C%20not%20only%20on%20the%20streets%20and%20in%20residential%20areas%20but%20also%20within%20government%20premises.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20General%20Administration%20Department%20has%20issued%20an%20order%20forming%20a%20committee%20of%2015%20members%2C%20including%20IAS%20officers%20up%20to%20the%20level%20of%20Additional%20Chief%20Secretary.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%2021%2C000%20dog%20bite%20cases%20have%20been%20reported%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20annually.%20In%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20stray%20dogs%20have%20killed%20five%20people%20including%20those%20who%20died%20from%20rabies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bhopal%20alone%2C%20hospitals%20receive%20an%20average%20of%2055%20cases%20of%20dog%20bites%20daily.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%201%2C%20Kunal%20from%20Lalghati%20in%20Bhopal%2C%20was%20mauled%20by%20a%20dog%2C%20requiring%20eight%20stitches.%20Five%20days%20later%2C%2016-year-old%20Ravi%20Sahu%20was%20attacked%20by%20stray%20dogs%20while%20visiting%20a%20shrine%20in%20Raisen%20with%20his%20family.%20On%20July%209%2C%20a%20man%20in%20Sethani%20Ghat%2C%20Hoshangabad%20was%20attacked%20by%20stray%20dogs%2C%20resulting%20in%20deep%20wounds%20on%20his%20leg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20government%20says%20the%20decision%20was%20driven%20by%20alarming%20data%2C%20the%20opposition%20claims%20it%20highlights%20governmental%20failures.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20taken%20this%20decision%20after%20thoroughly%20examining%20our%20data.%20Our%20priority%20is%20to%20save%20lives%2C%20which%20is%20why%20we%20have%20formed%20this%20committee%20of%20officers%2C%26quot%3B%20Animal%20husbandry%20minister%20Lakhan%20Patel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20situation%20on%20ground%20is%20dire.%20While%20the%20Bhopal%20Municipal%20Corporation's%20shelter%20home%20is%20overcrowded%20with%20stray%20dogs%2C%20dozens%20of%20people%20queue%20up%20every%20day%20in%20hospitals%20to%20get%20rabies%20injections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHospital%20data%20reveals%20alarming%20figures.%20In%202022%2C%20over%208%2C124%20dog%20bite%20incidents%20were%20recorded%20and%20in%202023%2C%20the%20number%20almost%20doubled%20to%2016%2C387.%20%C2%A0In%20the%20first%20five%20months%20of%202024%2C%20as%20many%20as%207%2C728%20cases%20of%20dog%20bites%20have%20been%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20organisations%20working%20for%20animal%20welfare%20have%20welcomed%20the%20decision.%20%26quot%3BThis%20government%20step%20is%20commendable.%20These%20senior%20officials%20will%20make%20good%20decisions%20and%20solve%20the%20problems%2C%26quot%3B%20Swati%20Gaurav%2C%20President%2C%20People%20for%20Animals%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721467020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2018-05%2Fstray-dogs-generic_650x400_71525256961.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-madhya-pradesh-panel-of-ias-officers-to-tackle-stray-dog-menace-6147302%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20government%20has%20appointed%20seven%20senior%20IAS%20officers%20to%20manage%20the%20escalating%20stray%20dog%20menace%20across%20the%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-madhya-pradesh-panel-of-ias-officers-to-tackle-stray-dog-menace-6147302%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-madhya-pradesh-panel-of-ias-officers-to-tackle-stray-dog-menace-6147302%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-madhya-pradesh-panel-of-ias-officers-to-tackle-stray-dog-menace-6147302%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ukrainian%20nationalist%20ex-MP%20shot%20dead%20in%20Lviv%20street%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721466942000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F3225%2Flive%2F6d683790-4671-11ef-bae0-5dac1fe394f9.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcp387p1zrgpo%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Iryna%20Farion%20caused%20controversy%20by%20suggesting%20that%20%E2%80%9Ctrue%20patriots%E2%80%9D%20of%20Ukraine%20should%20not%20speak%20Russian%20in%20any%20situation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A28%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcp387p1zrgpo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcp387p1zrg