%20Rally%20Won't%20Stop%20Trump%20From%20Rallying%20For%20Guns%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F6t6c0qng_trump_625x300_20_July_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncendiary%20battle%20cries%20fill%20the%20air%20as%20two%20opposing%20camps%20get%20ready%20for%20a%20face-off.%20Both%20sides%20have%20their%20chants%20and%20are%20blowing%20their%20trumpets%2C%20and%20they%20see%20the%20other%20as%20antithetical%20to%20their%20beliefs.%20It's%20reminiscent%20of%20warring%20houses%20from%C2%A0%3Cem%3EGame%20of%20Thrones%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20Viking%20duels%20from%20days%20of%20yore.%20But%20this%20isn't%20a%20mediaeval%20tale%2C%20it's%20a%20modern-day%20spectacle.%20Welcome%20to%20an%20election%20year%20in%20the%20United%20States%20of%20America%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmerica%20has%20long%20been%20a%20two-party%20system%2C%20but%20what%20we%20now%20have%20is%20a%20stark%20Manichean%20duopoly%2C%20driven%20by%20an%20ideological%20civil%20war.%20Each%20of%20the%20two%20warring%20parties%20believes%20that%20its%20own%20vision%20of%20America%20must%20be%20saved%20anyhow%2C%20and%20for%20that%20to%20happen%2C%20the%20other%20side%20must%20be%20vanquished%20at%20all%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20'Butler%20Bullet'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20rally%20in%20Butler%2C%20Pennsylvania%2C%20on%20July%2013%20turned%20into%20a%20nightmare%20as%20a%20lone%20gunman%2C%20Thomas%20Matthew%20Crooks%2C%20a%2020-year-old%20from%20Bethel%20Park%2C%20opened%20fire.%20It%20was%20a%20shot%20that%20was%20heard%20around%20the%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20time%20when%20many%20Democrats%20-%20one%20poll%20says%2065%25%20of%20registered%20Democrats%20-%20want%20Joe%20Biden%20to%20bite%20the%20bullet%20and%20make%20way%20for%20another%20candidate%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20took%20a%20literal%20bullet.%20Fortunately%2C%20no%20lasting%20damage%20was%20done%20to%20the%20former%20President%20as%20the%20bullet%20grazed%20his%20right%20ear.%20However%2C%20sadly%2C%20a%20rally%20attendee%20was%20killed%20and%20two%20others%20were%20critically%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%2C%20Vice-President%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20and%20former%20President%20Barack%20Obama%2C%20all%20passed%20on%20their%20concern%20for%20Trump's%20safety%20and%20unequivocal%20condemnation%20of%20the%20heinous%20attack%20-%20and%20rightly%20so.%20A%20deep%20sense%20of%20reflection%20ensued%2C%20and%20the%20American%20shibboleth%20acknowledged%20that%20this%20was%20not%20who%20they%20were.%20After%20all%2C%20in%20a%20robust%20democracy%2C%20the%20call%20is%20always%20for%20ballots%20over%20bullets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20lot%20to%20unpack%20here.%20History%20is%20a%20good%20teacher%20(even%20though%20in%20America%2C%20the%20phrase%20%26quot%3Bit's%20history%26quot%3B%20may%20often%20be%20used%20dismissively).%20Most%20millennial%20Americans%20-%20and%20certainly%20Trump's%20newly%20anointed%20running%20mate%2C%20Ohio%20Senator%20J.D.%20Vance%20-%20weren't%20even%20born%20when%20Republican%20messiah%20Ronald%20Reagan%20survived%20an%20assassination%20attempt%20in%201981.%20Some%20of%20Reagan's%20predecessors%2C%20like%20Abraham%20Lincoln%2C%20James%20Garfield%2C%20William%20McKinley%2C%20and%2C%20of%20course%2C%20John%20F.%20Kennedy%2C%20weren't%20as%20lucky%20as%20him%20(it's%20another%20thing%20that%20Reagan%20probably%20wouldn't%20recognise%20the%20Republican%20Party%20and%20what%20it%20has%20become%20today).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecret%20Service%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Secret%20Service%20has%20come%20under%20fire%20(no%20pun%20intended)%20and%20is%20being%20castigated%20for%20its%20failure%20to%20secure%20the%20premises%20and%20prevent%20an%20active%20shooter%20from%20getting%20within%20striking%20range%20of%20a%20former%20President.%20Ironically%2C%20the%20Service%20was%20formed%20the%20same%20year%20as%20President%20Lincoln's%20assassination%2C%20but%20their%20primary%20duty%20back%20then%20wasn't%20protecting%20presidents%2C%20vice-presidents%2C%20former%20presidents%2C%20or%20presidential%20candidates.%20Instead%2C%20the%20Service%20was%20under%20the%20U.S.%20Treasury%20and%20tasked%20with%20eliminating%20counterfeiting%2C%20a%20problem%20that%20emerged%20from%20the%20ashes%20of%20the%20Civil%20War.%20It%20was%20only%20after%20the%20assassination%20of%20McKinley%20in%201901%20that%20the%20Secret%20Service%20was%20entrusted%20with%20the%20protection%20of%20Presidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'America%20Dodged%20A%20Bullet%20Too'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Cem%3ECNN%3C%2Fem%3E%20political%20commentator%20Van%20Jones%20pointed%20out%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20wasn't%20just%20Donald%20Trump%20who%20narrowly%20dodged%20a%20bullet%2C%20but%20America%20too%26quot%3B.%20It%20wouldn't%20be%20wrong%20to%20think%20about%20the%20dangerous%20anarchy%20that%20could%20have%20unfolded%20had%20things%20gone%20south.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20don't%20have%20to%20look%20too%20far%20either.%20In%202021%2C%20when%20Donald%20Trump%20refused%20to%20accept%20the%20electoral%20outcome%20and%20urged%20his%20supporters%20to%20%26quot%3Btake%20back%20our%20country%26quot%3B%3F%20As%20Congress%20commenced%20an%20exercise%20to%20determine%20the%20peaceful%20transfer%20of%20power%2C%20an%20unruly%20pro-Trump%20mob%20stormed%20the%20Capitol%2C%20temporarily%20suspending%20the%20democratic%20process.%20Trump's%20supporters%2C%20who%20at%20one%20point%20had%20clamoured%20for%20a%20wall%20to%20be%20built%20to%20keep%20people%20out%2C%20wasted%20no%20time%20in%20climbing%20the%20walls%20of%20the%20Capitol.%20America's%20literal%20political%20and%20democratic%20edifice%20was%20breached%20and%20is%20now%20forever%20codified%20as%20the%20insurrection%20of%20January%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20Trump's%20running%20mate%20on%20the%20ballot%20was%20once%20a%20'Never%20Trumper'%20and%20had%20openly%20called%20him%20a%20threat%20to%20democracy.%20But%20flip-flopping%20is%20common%20in%20politics%2C%20especially%20when%20it's%20a%20ticket%20to%20the%20top%20on%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Was%20Crooks%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConspiracy%20theories%20abound%2C%20though%20the%20motive%20behind%20Crooks'%20action%20is%20not%20known%20yet.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnCrooks%20was%20a%20registered%20Republican%2C%20who%20used%20an%20AR-15%20assault%20rifle%20that%20many%20have%20sought%20to%20ban%20and%20many%20from%20the%20core%20Grand%20Old%20Party%20(GOP)%20base%20have%20continuously%20defended.%20The%20irony%20is%20that%20the%20GOP%2C%20which%20has%20long%20considered%20itself%20pro-life%2C%20has%20also%20been%20pro-guns.%20It's%20a%20party%20that%20has%20unequivocally%20backed%20gun%20ownership%20as%20a%20way%20of%20life%2C%20espousing%20guns%2C%20glory%2C%20and%20god-fearing%20Americans.%20The%20First%20Amendment%20protects%20free%20speech%2C%20press%2C%20assembly%2C%20and%20religion%2C%20while%20the%20Second%20Amendment%20allows%20most%20people%20in%20the%20United%20States%20to%20lock%20and%20load.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump's%20'Revenge'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20political%20pundits%20have%20critiqued%20Trump%20for%20stoking%20a%20febrile%20and%20hostile%20environment%20and%20encouraging%20violent%20tendencies%20among%20his%20base.%20Trump%20himself%20has%20brazenly%20indicated%20intentions%20of%20governing%20with%20a%20vendetta%20and%20inflicting%20%26quot%3Brevenge%26quot%3B%20on%20those%20who%20crossed%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recently%20concluded%20Republican%20convention%20in%20Milwaukee%20was%20perhaps%20a%20sign%20of%20the%20GOP's%20post-Butler%20outlook.%20It%20was%20almost%20a%20dystopian%20MAGA%20gathering.%20The%20four-day%20convention%20had%20different%20MAGA%20themes%20for%20each%20day%3A%20Monday%20was%20%26quot%3BMake%20America%20Wealthy%20Once%20Again%26quot%3B%2C%20Tuesday%20was%20%26quot%3BMake%20America%20Safe%20Once%20Again%26quot%3B%2C%20Wednesday%20was%20%26quot%3BMake%20America%20Strong%20Once%20Again%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20Thursday%2C%20the%20final%20day%2C%20was%20the%20cherry%20on%20the%20cake%20-%20%26quot%3BMake%20America%20Great%20Once%20Again%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20aftermath%20of%20the%20Butler%20bullet%20is%20such%20that%20Trump%20no%20longer%20needs%20to%20appeal%20to%20a%20Republican%20base.%20Instead%2C%20it's%20old-time%20Republicans%20who%20are%20now%20appealing%20to%20Trump's%20base.%20He%20has%20won%20the%20Republican%20nomination%20for%20Commander-in-Chief%20for%20an%20unprecedented%20third%20time%20and%20closed%20the%20convention%20with%20a%20speech%20that%20evoked%20a%20Lazarus-like%20rising%20sermon%20and%20mentioned%20the%20events%20of%20Saturday%2C%20using%20the%20event%20as%20a%20metaphor%20for%20how%20he%20will%20not%20be%20taken%20down.%20On%20that%20fateful%20day%2C%20Trump%20with%20a%20bloodied%20ear%20and%20red%20stains%20on%20his%20face%2C%20held%20a%20defiant%20fist%20and%20yelled%2C%20%26quot%3BFight!%26quot%3B%20as%20the%20Secret%20Service%20fought%20to%20cover%20him%20and%20take%20him%20off%20the%20podium%20when%20he%20was%20shot.%20It's%20now%20the%20image%20of%20the%20year.%20Political%20pundits%20see%20the%20unfortunate%20episode%20as%20one%20that%20will%20further%20solidify%20Trump's%20base%20and%20give%20him%20a%20chance%20at%20doing%20a%20Grover%20Cleveland%20and%20serving%20non-consecutive%20terms%20in%20the%20Oval%20Office.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20about%20gun%20laws%3F%20Well%2C%20that's%20like%20a%20bad%20playlist%20on%20repeat%2C%20with%20several%20lawmakers%2C%20mostly%20from%20the%20GOP%2C%20giving%20anodyne%20homilies%20after%20every%20shooting.%20%26quot%3BThe%20only%20thing%20that%20stops%20a%20bad%20guy%20with%20a%20gun%20is%20a%20good%20guy%20with%20a%20gun%26quot%3B.%20Little%20reason%20to%20assume%20the%20events%20of%20Butler%2C%20Pennsylvania%2C%20will%20bring%20about%20a%20change%20in%20their%20approach%20to%20stricter%20gun%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20as%20we%20speak%20about%20the%20bullet%2C%20it's%20fair%20to%20be%20reminded%20that%20Trump%2C%20in%20his%20speech%20at%20the%20National%20Rifle%20Association%20(NRA)%20convention%20just%20weeks%20before%20the%20Butler%20attack%2C%20had%20brazenly%20said%20that%20he%20would%20be%20the%20best%20friend%20in%20the%20White%20House%20for%20gun%20owners%2C%20and%20that%20%26quot%3BJoe%20Biden%20was%20coming%20for%20their%20guns%26quot%3B.%20Irony%2C%20loud%20and%20piercing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Akshobh%20Giridharadas%20is%20a%20Washington%2C%20D.C.-based%20policy%20professional.%20He%20was%20a%20former%20journalist%20based%20out%20of%20Singapore%20and%20was%20a%20reporter%20and%20producer%20with%20Channel%20News%20Asia%20(CNA)%20covering%20international%20business%20news.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721458320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F1avci8fo_trump_625x300_20_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fa-gun-at-a-trump-rally-wont-stop-trump-from-rallying-for-guns-6146407%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trump%2C%20in%20his%20speech%20at%20the%20National%20Rifle%20Association%20(NRA)%20convention%20just%20weeks%20before%20the%20Butler%20attack%2C%20had%20brazenly%20said%20that%20he%20would%20be%20the%20best%20friend%20in%20the%20White%20House%20for%20gun%20owners.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fa-gun-at-a-trump-rally-wont-stop-trump-from-rallying-for-guns-6146407%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww