tres.%20This%20timing%20coincides%20with%20heavy%20rains%2C%20raising%20concerns%20about%20potential%20flooding.%20Mumbai%20and%20Palghar%20are%20under%20a%20yellow%20alert%2C%20while%20Thane%20district%20faces%20a%20more%20severe%20orange%20alert.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYesterday%2C%20Mumbai's%20central%20recorded%20an%20average%20rainfall%20of%2078%20mm%2C%20while%20eastern%20and%20western%20Mumbai%20recorded%2057%20mm%20and%2067%20mm%2C%20respectively.%20The%20weather%20office%20has%20forecast%20moderate%20to%20heavy%20rains%20in%20the%20city%2C%20indicating%20that%20the%20downpour%20is%20likely%20to%20continue%2C%20exacerbating%20the%20current%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMumbai's%20public%20transport%20services%20were%20significantly%20impacted.%20The%20incessant%20rain%20has%20led%20to%20waterlogging%20on%20roads%20and%20railway%20tracks%2C%20causing%20delays%20in%20suburban%20train%20services%2C%20which%20were%20running%2015%20to%2020%20minutes%20behind%20schedule.%20Water%20accumulation%20on%20the%20tracks%20at%20Chunabhatti%20on%20the%20Harbour%20line%2C%20compounded%20by%20high%20tide%2C%20has%20slowed%20train%20movements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20line%20of%20the%20Central%20Railway%20faced%20additional%20delays%20due%20to%20a%20technical%20glitch%20in%20a%20train%20engine.%20The%20Western%20Railway%20has%20stated%20that%20its%20suburban%20services%20are%20running%2C%20though%20not%20without%20challenges.%20All%20three%20lines%20-%20Central%2C%20Western%2C%20and%20Harbour%20-%20are%20running%2010%20minutes%20late.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Andheri%20subway%2C%20a%20critical%20link%20for%20commuters%2C%20was%20closed%20due%20to%20significant%20waterlogging.%20The%20continuous%20rainfall%20has%20filled%20the%20subway%20with%20water%2C%20making%20it%20impassable.%20However%2C%20it%20was%20opened%20later%20in%20the%20day%2C%20once%20the%20water%20subsided.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeavy%20rain%20has%20battered%20Thane%20district%20since%20midnight.%20Water%20has%20accumulated%20at%20the%20Thane%20Vandana%20bus%20depot%20and%20the%20local%20market%2C%20leading%20to%20disruption%20in%20daily%20activities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Nagpur%2C%20heavy%20rain%20warnings%20have%20led%20to%20the%20closure%20of%20schools%20across%20the%20district.%20Nagpur%20District%20Collector%20Dr%20Vipin%20Itankar%20told%20NDTV%20that%20all%20schools%20will%20remain%20shut%20today.%20Although%20flight%20schedules%20at%20Nagpur%20airport%20remain%20unaffected%2C%20the%20situation%20in%20Bhiwandi%20city%20is%20critical.%20Since%20morning%2C%20heavy%20rain%20has%20caused%20water%20accumulation%20in%20several%20parts%20of%20the%20city%2C%20including%20knee-deep%20water%20in%20the%20Teen%20Batti%20area%20of%20Sabzi%20Bazar.%20Many%20low-lying%20areas%20are%20at%20risk%20of%20water%20entering%20homes%20and%20shops%20if%20the%20rains%20persist.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721453580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fqmcgs7do_mumbai-subway-_625x300_20_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmumbai-news%2Fheavy-rain-in-mumbai-causes-traffic-chaos-andheri-subway-flooded-6146078%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Overnight%20and%20continuing%20morning%20rain%20have%20brought%20Mumbai%20to%20a%20standstill%2C%20disrupting%20public%20transport%20services%20and%20causing%20inconvenience%20to%20countless%20commuters.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmumbai-news%2Fheavy-rain-in-mumbai-causes-traffic-chaos-andheri-subway-flooded-6146078%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmumbai-news%2Fheavy-rain-in-mumbai-causes-traffic-chaos-andheri-subway-flooded-6146078%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmumbai-news%2Fheavy-rain-in-mumbai-causes-traffic-chaos-andheri-subway-flooded-6146078%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP%20vs%20BJP%20In%20Bengal%20Over%20Differences%20In%20'Sabka%20Saath%2C%20Sabka%20Vikas'%20Outlook%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20Minority%20Morcha%20national%20president%2C%20Jamal%20Siddiqui%2C%20has%20said%20that%20%3Cem%3E'Sabka%20Saath%2C%20Sabka%20Vikas'%3C%2Fem%3E%20(development%20and%20trust%20for%20all)%20is%20the%20soul%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%20that%20just%20as%20a%20body%20is%20useless%20without%20a%20soul%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20nothing%20without%20'Sabka%20Saath%2C%20Sabka%20Vikas'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20with%20ANI%2C%20Mr%20Siddiqui%20shared%20his%20views%20on%20a%20comment%20made%20by%20West%20Bengal%20BJP%20leader%20Suvendu%20Adhikari.%20He%20said%20that%20Mr%20Adhikari's%20statement%2C%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BJo%20humare%20saath%2C%20hum%20unke%20saath%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20made%20impulsively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuvendu%20Adhikari%20is%20new%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20having%20joined%20only%20a%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20may%20still%20be%20influenced%20by%20his%20past%20political%20experiences%20in%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%2C%20where%20the%20focus%20was%20solely%20on%20gaining%20power.%20As%20Mr%20Adhikari%20understands%20the%20BJP%20better%2C%20he%20will%20realise%20that%20the%20party%20works%20differently...%20Adhikari%20had%20also%20clarified%20that%20his%20statement%20was%20misrepresented%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Siddiqui%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuvendu%20Adhikari's%20statement%20was%20made%20in%20a%20moment%20of%20emotional%20distress%20and%20disappointment%2C%20but%20the%20BJP%20doesn't%20operate%20on%20such%20emotional%20impulses%20and%20instead%20focuses%20on%20taking%20everyone%20along%2C%20regardless%20of%20their%20political%20affiliations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20leader%20said%20that%20the%20party%20was%20formed%20to%20fulfil%20the%20dreams%20of%20Pandit%20Deendayal%20Upadhyaya%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B'Sabka%20Saath%2C%20Sabka%20Vikas'%20is%20the%20soul%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20just%20like%20a%20body%20is%20useless%20without%20a%20soul.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20nothing%20without%20%3Cem%3E'Sabka%20Saath%2C%20Sabka%20Vikas'%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20BJP%20was%20not%20formed%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20gaining%20power%20but%20to%20fulfil%20the%20dreams%20of%20Pandit%20Deendayal%20Upadhyaya%20and%20his%20ideology%20of%20'Antyodaya'%20(uplifting%20the%20last%20person%20in%20the%20queue).%20The%20goal%20of%20the%20BJP%20is%20to%20bring%20a%20smile%20to%20the%20face%20of%20the%20most%20oppressed%2C%20suffering%2C%20deprived%2C%20and%20troubled%20person%20in%20society.%20This%20is%20the%20purpose%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20it%20is%20moving%20forward%20with%20this%20objective%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20added%20that%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20the%20biggest%20beneficiaries%20of%20the%20central%20schemes%20have%20been%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPower%20is%20only%20a%20means%20of%20service%20for%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party.%20We%20have%20always%20been%20taught%20that%20we%20should%20not%20engage%20in%20vote-bank%20politics.%20We%20need%20to%20win%20votes%20in%20elections%20because%2C%20through%20votes%2C%20we%20will%20come%20to%20power%20and%20be%20able%20to%20serve%20the%20public%20well.%20But%20even%20for%20those%20who%20do%20not%20vote%20for%20us%2C%20who%20are%20misled%2C%20and%20who%20consider%20us%20enemies%2C%20we%20must%20embrace%20everyone%2C%20serve%20everyone%2C%20give%20justice%20to%20everyone%2C%20and%20take%20everyone%20along.%20Our%20honourable%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20prioritised%20this%20in%20his%20%3Cem%3EGarib%20Kalyan%20Yojana%3C%2Fem%3E.%20He%20has%20said%2C%20%3Cem%3E'Sabka%20Saath%2C%20Sabka%20Vikas%2C%20Sabka%20Paryas'%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20In%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20provided%20services%2C%20and%20the%20biggest%20beneficiaries%20have%20been%20Muslims.%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccusing%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20of%20misleading%20minorities%2C%20the%20BJP%20leader%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20education%20in%20Muslim%20society%2C%20and%20we%20(the%20BJP)%20also%20have%20small%20shortcomings.%20We%2C%20the%20people%20of%20the%20Minority%20Morcha%2C%20are%20part%20of%20society%20and%20couldn't%20explain%20our%20thoughts%20and%20ideas%20well%20to%20them.%20The%20India%20Alliance%20(opposition%20parties)%20misled%20them%3B%20they%20are%20like%20hungry%20wolves%20who%20only%20want%20power%2C%20and%20that's%20why%20they%20(Muslims)%20got%20confused%20and%20went%20astray.%20But%20they%20are%20still%20our%20brothers.%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20said%20that%20we%20will%20support%20those%20who%20voted%20for%20us%20and%20also%20those%20who%20didn't%3B%20we%20will%20take%20everyone%20along%20the%20path%20of%20development%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20leader%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20West%20Bengal%20Assembly%2C%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%2C%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20%26quot%3Bshould%20now%20stop%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BSabka%20Saath%2C%20Sabka%20Vikas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuvendu%20Adhikari%20asserted%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Btime%20has%20come%20when%20the%20party%20should%20prioritise%20those%20who%20support%20them.%26quot%3B%20During%20the%20event%2C%20he%20also%20chanted%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BJai%20Shri%20Ram%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20declared%20his%20intention%20to%20%26quot%3Bprotect%20Hindus%20and%20the%20Constitution.%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20a%20BJP%20state%20executive%20committee%20meeting%2C%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20need%20to%20talk%20about%20%3Cem%3ESabka%20Saath%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3ESabka%20Vikas%3C%2Fem%3E.%20We%20will%20decide%20who%20supports%20us%2C%20and%20we%20will%20support%20them.%20Stop%20this%20talk%20of%20%3Cem%3ESabka%20Saath%2C%20Sabka%20Vikas%3C%2Fem%3E.%20There%20is%20no%20need%20for%20a%20minority%20front.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20controversy%20erupted%20over%20his%20remarks%2C%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%20said%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3ESabka%20Saath%2C%20Sabka%20Vikas%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20PM%20Modi's%20slogan%2C%20and%20it%20won't%20change%20with%20my%20words.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20slogan%20was%20given%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20it%20remains.%20As%20a%20BJP%20functionary%2C%20with%20heavy%20pain%2C%20I%20kept%20my%20point%20forward%20that%20the%20BJP's%20state%20unit%20should%20stand%20with%20the%20party%20workers%20and%20not%20with%20those%20who%20do%20not%20stand%20with%20the%20BJP.%20This%20is%20a%20political%20statement%20and%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi's%20%3Cem%3E'Sabka%20sath%20sabka%20vikas'%20slogan.%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20visit%20my%20constituency%2C%20both%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20benefit%20from%20all%20the%20development%20work.%20Even%20then%2C%20we%20get%20to%20hear%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20a%20Hindu%20party...%20We%20are%20shown%20black%20flags%20and%20stones%20are%20pelted%20on%20our%20vehicles.%20Whatever%20we%20have%20done%20so%20far%20is%20for%20every%20citizen%20of%20the%20country%2C%20irrespective%20of%20religion.%20My%20statements%20are%20personal%20and%20have%20no%20relation%20to%20the%20party's%20thoughts.%20There%20was%20a%20minority%20%3Cem%3Emorcha%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20my%20constituency.%20I%20celebrated%20Eid%20with%20700%20people%20in%20the%20Milan%20Utsav.%20And%20BJP%20candidate%20Abhijit%20Ganguly%20did%20not%20even%20get%20one%20vote.%20Communal%20voting%20greatly%20affected%20the%20BJP%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3E'Sabka%20Saath%2C%20Sabka%20Vikas'%3C%2Fem%3E%20slogan%20was%20given%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%202014%20to%20promote%20inclusive%20and%20holistic%20development%20of%20all%20Indians%2C%20irrespective%20of%20caste%20and%20religion.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721453280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F5up33de4_suvendu-adhikari-vs-jamal-siddiqui-bengal-bjp_625x300_20_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-vs-bjp-in-bengal-over-differences-in-sabka-saath-sabka-vikas-outlook-6144355%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP's%20Minority%20Morcha%20national%20president%2C%20Jamal%20Siddiqui%2C%20has%20said%20that%20'Sabka%20Saath%2C%20Sabka%20Vikas'%20(development%20and%20trust%20for%20all)%20is%20the%20soul%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-vs-bjp-in-bengal-over-differences-in-sabka-saath-sabka-vikas-outlook-6144355%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-vs-bjp-in-bengal-over-differences-in-sabka-saath-sabka-vikas-outlook-6144355%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-vs-bjp-in-bengal-over-differences-in-sabka-saath-sabka-vikas-outlook-6144355%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bridge%20collapses%20in%20China%20-%20president%20orders%20all-out%20rescue%20effort%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721452320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F07%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-china-bridge-collapse_6633381.jpg%3F20240720072013%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fbridge-collapses-in-china-at-least-11-people-dead-and-dozens-missing-13181707%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20least%2011%20people%