Url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fjapanese-gymnastics-team-captain-withdraws-from-paris-olympics-after-smoking-and-drinking-13180959%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Unexpected%20Origin%20Stories%20of%20Chicken%20Tikka%20Masala%20%26amp%3B%20a%20Must-Try%20Recipe%20by%20Chef%20Ranveer%20Brar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAnyone%20who%E2%80%99s%20on%20their%20early%20morning%20jog%20or%20a%20drive%20in%20South%20Manchester%2C%20England%20has%20more%20often%20than%20not%20had%20the%20feeling%20of%20having%20just%20been%20swallowed%20up%20by%20an%20inter-dimensional%20portal.%20This%20feeling%20peaks%20at%20Wilmslow%20Road%2C%20which%20runs%20through%20the%20centre%20of%20Rusholme.%20In%20an%20instant%2C%20the%20physical%20landscape%20of%20top-notch%2C%20stone-structure%2C%20Michelin-starred%20fine-dining%20restaurants%20with%20coiffured%20waiters%20gives%20way%20to%20sprightly%2C%20pop-up%20eateries%20with%20attractive%20hoardings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWelcome%20to%20%E2%80%98The%20Curry%20Mile%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20an%20area%20of%20England%20that%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20the%20largest%20concentration%20of%20South%20Asian%20restaurants%20in%20the%20United%20Kingdom.%20Since%20the%2050s%20%E2%80%94%20when%20this%20area%20became%20a%20boomtown%20of%20textile%20mills%20recruiting%20men%20from%20South%20Asia%20who%20went%20on%20to%20set%20up%20their%20restaurants%20here%20%E2%80%94%20Curry%20Mile%20has%20become%20synonymous%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F356455%2Fbest-breakfast-places-in-new-delhi-shops-cafes-restaurants-chhole-bhature-pancakes-kachori%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20food%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKebabs%20%3C%2Fem%3E(minced%20meat%20cooked%20on%20skewers)%2C%20grills%2C%20%3Cem%3Eshawarma%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20Middle%20Eastern%20dish%20consisting%20of%20meat%20that%20is%20cut%20into%20thin%20slices%2C%20stacked%20in%20an%20inv