-bag-for-homeless-during-winter%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elitres%20of%20water%20wasted%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20unfair%20wages%20paid%20to%20those%20involved.%20If%20you%20look%20at%20it%20from%20this%20perspective%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20agree%20that%20nothing%20is%20%E2%80%98cheap%E2%80%99%20even%20when%20it%20appears%20to%20be.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20two-decade-long%20experience%20in%20the%20development%20sector%2C%20during%20which%20she%20was%20associated%20with%20UNICEF%20and%20other%20affluent%20names%2C%20shaped%20her%20way%20of%20thinking%20and%20living.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsustainable-homestay-2_11zon-1721041018.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20mother-daughter%20duo%20transformed%20the%20barren%20land%20into%20a%20thriving%20organic%20farm%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsustainable-homestay-2_11zon-1721041018.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsustainable-homestay-2_11zon-1721041018-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsustainable-homestay-2_11zon-1721041018-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsustainable-homestay-2_11zon-1721041018-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsustainable-homestay-2_11zon-1721041018-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356898%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20mother-daughter%20duo%20transformed%20the%20barren%20land%20into%20a%20thriving%20organic%20farm%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Disha%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3