ID-19%20pandemic%20hit%2C%20and%20we%20got%20to%20work%20from%20home.%20My%20girlfriend%20(now%20wife)%20and%20I%20started%20taking%20small%20trips%20around%20Managluru%20when%20the%20restrictions%20eased%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20Tejas%20already%20had%20a%20YouTube%20channel%20where%20he%20did%20some%20moto-vlogging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20focus%20more%20on%20creating%20content%2C%20dedicating%20a%20couple%20of%20hours%20each%20day%20to%20filming%20and%20editing.%20It%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20a%20planned%20journey%20to%20becoming%20content%20creators%3B%20it%20just%20happened%20as%20we%20kept%20making%20videos%20and%20some%20of%20them%20went%20viral%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20how%20he%20manages%20travelling%20with%20his%20full-time%20job%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20very%20challenging%2C%20but%20we%20manage%20by%20prioritising%20travel%20over%20other%20activities.%20Both%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20have%20flexible%20jobs%20that%20allow%20us%20to%20work%20from%20anywhere.%20We%20have%20supportive%20managers%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20easier%20to%20get%20time-off%20when%20needed.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%E2%80%99re%20travelling%2C%20we%20wake%20up%20early%2C%20explore%20the%20place%2C%20and%20then%20start%20working%20around%2011%20am.%20We%20work%20until%20about%206pm%2C%20take%20small%20breaks%20in%20between%2C%20and%20then%20spend%20an%20hour%20or%20so%20editing%20videos%20at%20night.%20It%E2%80%99s%20all%20about%20prioritising%20travel%20and%20making%20the%20most%20of%20our%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20has%20travelled%20to%20most%20states%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20initial%20goal%20was%20to%20cover%20ten%20states%20in%20a%20year.%20Recently%2C%20we%20went%20from%20Mangaluru%20to%20Srinagar.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20covere