%20of%20the%20contest%2C%20thus%2C%20was%20to%20send%20out%20a%20clear%20message%20that%20these%20homes%20are%20no%20longer%20a%20sidenote%20in%20the%20margins.%20They%20hold%20the%20transformative%20power%20to%20shape%20the%20future%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20economy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20contest%20like%20this%20provides%20the%20opportunity%20for%20existing%20and%20new%20entrepreneurs%20and%20business%20leaders%20to%20move%20the%20gaze%20away%20from%20big%20cities%20and%20disposable%20incomes%20to%20small%20towns%20and%20core%20services%2C%20and%20they%E2%80%99ll%20find%20that%20the%20market%20potential%20is%20immense.%20Enmasse%20World%20calls%20this%20the%20Economic%20Power%20of%20Industrious%20Communities%2C%20or%20the%20EPIC%20Opportunity.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20new%20age%20creed%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%202022%20story%2C%20%3Cem%3EForbes%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20called%20owners%20of%20small%20home%20businesses%20the%20%E2%80%98OG%20entrepreneurs%E2%80%99.%20The%20moniker%20is%20backed%20by%20statistics.%20According%20to%20a%202024%20report%20by%20%3Cem%3EPraxis%20Global%20Alliance%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20Enmasse%20World%2C%20in%20FY%202023%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20247%20million%20entrepreneurial%20households%20drove%20an%20%248.8%20trillion%20transaction%20value%20%E2%80%94%20with%20a%20significant%20portion%20being%20informal%20transactions%2C%20unleashing%20a%20new%20economic%20landscape.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20in%20home-owned%20businesses%20and%20their%20success%20are%20a%20nod%20to%20the%20notion%20that%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20economic%20prospects%20do%20not%20necessarily%20lie%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20commercial%20enterprises.%20But%20rather%2C%20that%20magic%20can%20often%20be%20brewed%20in%20the%20smallest%20of%20farms%20and%20home%20kitchens.%20That%E2%80%99s%20where%20India%E2%80%99s%20collective%20growth%20story%20is%20unfolding%2C%20every%20single%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Frural-startups-1-1720763650.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Yogesh%20Gawande%E2%80%99s%20Niyo-Farm%20Tech%20crafts%20innovative%20agri-equipment%20for%20farmers.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Frural-startups-1-1720763650.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Frural-startups-1-1720763650-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Frural-startups-1-1720763650-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Frural-startups-1-1720763650-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Frural-startups-1-1720763650-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356679%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EYogesh%20Gawande%E2%80%99s%20Niyo-Farm%20Tech%20crafts%20innovative%20agri-equipment%20for%20farmers.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDreams%2C%20after%20all%2C%20do%20not%20need%20space%3B%20they%20only%20demand%20resilience.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20we%20celebrate%20these%20heroes%2C%20the%20journey%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20end%20here.%20It%20is%20just%20the%20beginning.%20The%20common%20misconception%20still%20says%20that%20individuals%20from%20such%20smaller%20towns%20and%20cities%20are%20an%20economic%20risk%20and%20that%20this%20segment%20is%20not%20ready%20for%20commercial%20engagement%2C%20for%20reasons%20such%20as%20the%20unwillingness%20or%20inability%20to%20